Label: Resource version feature value
Description: A controlled value that describes a resource version feature. Presence or absence of this element depends on the <ResourceVersionFeatureType>, since some features may not require an accompanying value, while others may require free text in <FeatureNote>, and others may have both a value and free text. Non-repeating.
Format: <dd>Dependent on the feature specified in <ResourceVersionFeatureType>; the feature value may or may not be taken from a code list</dd>
